                        <h5>sins-lab</h5>
                        <p>Research and development area in Cybersecurity, Web & Multiplatform Development, and Microservices Architecture at the Secure and Intelligent Networked Software Systems (sins-lab) laboratory, University of Beira Interior (UBI).</p>
                        <ul class="timeline-tags">
                            <li>Cybersecurity</li>
                            <li>Web Development</li>
                            <li>Microservices</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-date">2025 - Present</div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <h4>Team Leader & Software Developer</h4>
                        <h5>Cyber Crow Project</h5>
